query:
INSERT INTO categories_override (
                    user_id,
                    category_id,
                    color,
                    is_enabled
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4
                ) ON CONFLICT (
                    user_id,
                    category_id
                ) DO UPDATE SET
                    color = EXCLUDED.color,
                    is_enabled = EXCLUDED.is_enabled
